Name: nOfAllocatedInRep
Desc: Number of InReports which are currently allocated (i.e. which have been successfully created by the InFactory and not yet released)

Name: nOfAllocatedInCmd
Desc: Number of InCommands which are currently allocated (i.e. which have been successfully created by the InFactory and not yet released)

Name: nOfAllocatedOutCmp
Desc: Number of OutComponents which are currently allocated (i.e. which have been successfully created by the OutFactory and not yet released)

Name: nOfFailedInRep
Desc: Number of InReports whose creation by the InFactory failed

Name: nOfFailedInCmd
Desc: Number of InCommands whose creation by the InFactory failed

Name: nOfFailedOutCmp
Desc: Number of OutComponents whose creation by the OutFactory failed

Name: nOfTotAllocatedInRep
Desc: Number of InReports successfully created by the InFactory since application start

Name: nOfTotAllocatedInCmd
Desc: Number of InCommands successfully created by the InFactory since application start

Name: nOfTotAllocatedOutCmp
Desc: Number of OutComponents successfully created by the InFactory since application start

Name: nOfAccFailed
Desc: Number of commands which have failed their acceptance check since the application was last reset

Name: nOfStartFailed
Desc: Number of commands which have failed their Start Check since the application was last reset

Name: nOfPrgrFailed
Desc: Number of commands which have failed their Progress Check since the application was last reset

Name: nOfTermFailed
Desc: Number of commands which have failed their Termination Check since the application was last reset

Name: nOfReroutingFailed
Desc: Number of commands for which re-routing failed

Name: pcktIdAccFailed
Desc: Packet identifier of last command which failed its Acceptance Check

Name: pcktIdStartFailed
Desc: Packet identifier of last command which failed its Start Check

Name: pcktIdPrgrFailed
Desc: Packet identifier of last command which failed its Progress Check

Name: prgrStep
Desc: Identifier of the step at which the progress check was last verified (either failed or succeeded)

Name: pcktIdTermFailed
Desc: Packet identifier of last command which failed its Termination Check

Name: pcktIdReroutingFailed
Desc: Packet identifier of last command for which re-routing failed

Name: failCodeAccFailed
Desc: Failure code of last command which failed its Acceptance Check

Name: failCodeStartFailed
Desc: Failure code of last command which failed its Start Check

Name: failCodePrgrFailed
Desc: Failure code of last command which failed its Progress Check

Name: failCodeTermFailed
Desc: Failure code of last command which failed its Termination Check

Name: failDataAccFailed
Desc: Failure-related data item of last command which failed its Acceptance Check

Name: failDataStartFailed
Desc: Failure-related data item of last command which failed its Start Check

Name: failDataPrgrFailed
Desc: Failure-related data item of last command which failed its Progress Check

Name: failDataTermFailed
Desc: Failure-related data item of last command which failed its Termination Check
